powerpc/watchpoint: Rename current H_SET_MODE DAWR macro

Current H_SET_MODE hcall macro name for setting/resetting DAWR0 is
H_SET_MODE_RESOURCE_SET_DAWR. Add suffix 0 to macro name as well.

